title: Noctes Ambrosianæ.
author: Wilson, John
snippet: II The Fruid's su' o' sma' troots, and I sune had a string.

title: Noctes Ambrosianæ.
author: Wilson, John
snippet: Sae I just thocht I wad try the Fruid wi' the flee, and put on a professor.

title: Noctes Ambrosianæ.
author: Wilson, John
snippet: But I forgot I wasna on foot — the beast gotblawn, and coming up the Fruid, § reested wi' me on Garlet-Dod.
